{"tid":881483,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"因為我養你 所以你要聽我話","createTime":"2018-10-29T12:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T13:41:30.000Z","uid":180156,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a23ea6c1540675972fdffdc7e293ab3ae2303357","tid":881483,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"個合理性係邊到？"},{"pid":"c1fd83258dcd6c9b8d4e34f16536a5aa131e7299","tid":881483,"uid":2419,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T12:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/29/205949_8c5f3d1d52c145af2e59ffab0995e642.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F29%2F205949_8c5f3d1d52c145af2e59ffab0995e642.gif&h=e35ddefc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4135abec755ff7f3dd22ba4fb8fc678d1c811c09","tid":881483,"uid":180156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:05:02.000Z","msg":"例如 因為我養你 所以你唔準反駁我"},{"pid":"da52e41ebb89589009163a28d0ddd424e1ae3aea","tid":881483,"uid":192491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:09:02.000Z","msg":"冇合理性, 但有情理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0962ea31447a4353d1688d89c0a9354aef3fe5d","tid":881483,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:11:29.000Z","msg":"屋企人最鐘意講呢句<br />\n可以點駁？"},{"pid":"24468c36a7adc8c923d15c3479e4ec4f35db0d27","tid":881483,"uid":118271,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:12:09.000Z","msg":"即係好似你養寵物咁<br />\n啲狗主都好鍾意呼呼喝喝啲狗仔<br />\n<br />\n咪又係因為佢當咗自己係主人 俾佢住俾佢食  所以同你講呢句說話嘅人其實係當你係寵物<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35c7c218b64e5da79cb1f42872ea076ac4a7b0a","tid":881483,"uid":199211,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:50:14.000Z","msg":"通常無讀書嘅上一代都係咁撚on9"},{"pid":"4f2e05612d14a8a6f9a1667b250202698d815ca2","tid":881483,"uid":30831,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T15:14:46.000Z","msg":"有經濟能力就自己住 斷六親 零家用<br />\n佢對你不義咪咁囉<br />\n樓主可以當依家做緊一份未來每個月多兩千蚊洗嘅工作"},{"pid":"ef6e0556ecb5e364b67da24b08868b8ca6fd5f6f","tid":881483,"uid":125976,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a23ea6c1540675972fdffdc7e293ab3ae2303357","tid":881483,"uid":180156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"個合理性係邊到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:13:53.000Z","msg":"依個概念係建基於喺交易市場嘅概念上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n養者：<br />\n提供 =&gt; 資源俾被養者<br />\n要求 &lt;= 活得符合養者渴求嘅形象<br />\n<br />\n被養者：<br />\n收取 &lt;= 養者提供嘅資源<br />\n代價 =&gt; 活得符合養者渴求嘅形象<br />\n<br />\n就好似股票交易一樣，大家出買賣價，直到雙方接受為止。<br />\n<br />\n但好不幸地，如果係講梗父子 / 母子關係，依個係一個唔公平嘅交易，因為被養者冇權選擇出生與否<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426a3e857ad47e85dc9c0067c4ea3317117c6877","tid":881483,"uid":164980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:47:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f5efe28450b7937a874c77db9f918b39a278858","tid":881483,"uid":84797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c1fd83258dcd6c9b8d4e34f16536a5aa131e7299","tid":881483,"uid":2419,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T12:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/29/205949_8c5f3d1d52c145af2e59ffab0995e642.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F29%2F205949_8c5f3d1d52c145af2e59ffab0995e642.gif&h=e35ddefc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> seed?"},{"pid":"91ff9bd820771d8f9b4b782be43ab40947c9b88a","tid":881483,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:31:37.000Z"